summary: An ordinance relating to zoning and providing for the rezoning of Tract 66 of Kelsey's Brighton Beach Acre Tracts and Lots 21, 22 and west one-half of Lot 20, Block 32, Hill Tract Addition, with respect to Use and Area Districts, and amending Ordinance No.45382, as amended, by adding thereto two new sections numbered 2-191 and 17-140 respectively.
